Build kodex.idx from a compiled project's `SemanticDB` and Mill metadata

Usage: kodex index [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --idx <IDX>    Path to kodex.idx (default: .scalex/kodex.idx, or `KODEX_IDX` env var)
      --root <ROOT>  Workspace root (must contain Mill out/ directory) [default: .]
  -h, --help         Print help